{"tid":1250253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全力爭取成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T14:54:19.000Z","uid":116572,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aadc31f587a3d4989416ff55ca06c769eff47bcd","tid":1250253,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"哩個應該係最多人認同嘅共識嚟，無論和理非定勇武甚至乎一部分建制都唔反對<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅監警根本起唔到作用，而且要調查埋前因後果政府處理手法應該得哩個方法（更何況警察四大工會反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n至於其他訴求並非唔爭取，而係哩個應該係最多人認同嘅訴求，可以爭取到最多民意，成本亦都不大"},{"pid":"facb269b3da75904351f6d142f631e5a0b3b6afc","tid":1250253,"uid":134149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"就算係建制/藍絲 都體驗過警隊既不公<br />\n<br />\n加上612既事件，真係點講都講唔過去<br />\n<br />\n如果今次唔食正呢條水去檢討警權<br />\n<br />\n下次可能真係要實彈流血先再有機會"},{"pid":"fcdaabe805f909480da649daf9052c89f51d34f8","tid":1250253,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"睇下班高官成日係到就呢個話題擺龍門 你就知佢地幾撚怕呢個委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5990dae9276387bc26fce49fdbc90a4528493670","tid":1250253,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4af70bc096466eb4227bba30de701fa75164fac","tid":1250253,"uid":117673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"一定要成立 <br />\n受夠佢地啦 屌！"},{"pid":"f2d24823b3d044c8b74d90214b714984b7218fb5","tid":1250253,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcdaabe805f909480da649daf9052c89f51d34f8","tid":1250253,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"睇下班高官成日係到就呢個話題擺龍門 你就知佢地幾撚怕呢個委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比你成立左 班狗反咬主人都得<br />\n班高官怕無人保護"},{"pid":"85088db66409adf8ae094fd6054edffcc128659f","tid":1250253,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5386913b83e1ecf3f83adae519a2da3e40b4287","tid":1250253,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"212d8c2f17ecec9c3f7ad291bc379e08fbc1e131","tid":1250253,"uid":116572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四警協會反對獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰昨會見四個警隊職員協會代表，稱充份肯定各職級人員工作。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處處長盧偉聰昨與一眾警隊高層與四個警隊職員協會代表會面，盧充份肯定各職級人員在近日衝突的工作，並指派一個由行動處處長蕭澤頤率領的檢討委員會，全面檢討今次警方行動，免令警務人員受無理的指控。四個協會認為投訴警察機制行之有效，強烈反對成立獨立調查委員會調查事件。"},{"pid":"c961686c8e5b870766a3b27f8ae3f803c71fe2f5","tid":1250253,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b769667806c3d4ac6c3fd66c33aff7e85e82083","tid":1250253,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>律政司同警方都唔支持</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"737c2dd3c4f61b828bded3f18fa8364808f8b960","tid":1250253,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46c4aa12c2ccd00998be4ae2fe649705ebb47f7","tid":1250253,"uid":116572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:18:51.000